snippet.textDisplay:
I had it. I couldn't even get to my bathroom without gasping for air. Felt like something was sat on my chest for a few days and I had diapram pain from fighting to breathe & it lasted even when it went because I was that bad. 
Wouldnt wish it on anyone.
